name: 'photo_album.pnj' #009
description:
I stood alone before the sea late at night, on the Southeast coast of England, and in that darkness, against the roaring of waves and scattering of stones, I learned something about the unconscious mind... 

Each NFT represents a unique visual memory, deconstructed - or distilled - to basic pixelated components. Collect them all and build up a photo album of collective memories : )
